Olark Chat Integration for Elgg
---------------------------------
Install:
--------
1) Unzip olark_chat.zip in your elgg site's mod/ folder

2) Log into your site as admin and enable the plugin under Administration->Tools Administriation.

3) Follow the "Click here to obtain a key" link in the plugin setting or go to http://www.olark.com/?rid=mehatem to create an olark chat account. Your key can be found under the 'Chat Box' script code, it looks something like 'olark-0000-000-00-0000'

4) Enter your olark key in the textbox and click 'Save'. 

Support:
--------
If you have any questions, please sent an email to txtan@redmelonconsulting.com
